{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I am a reformed marketer,"},{"time":2000,"text":"and I now work in international development."},{"time":5000,"text":"In October, I spent some time in the Democratic Republic of Congo,"},{"time":8000,"text":"which is the [second] largest country in Africa."},{"time":10000,"text":"In fact, it's as large as Western Europe,"},{"time":13000,"text":"but it only has 300 miles of paved roads."},{"time":17000,"text":"The DRC is a dangerous place."},{"time":19000,"text":"In the past 10 years, five million people have died"},{"time":22000,"text":"due to a war in the east."},{"time":24000,"text":"But war isn't the only reason"},{"time":26000,"text":"that life is difficult in the DRC."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"There are many health issues as well."},{"time":30000,"text":"In fact, the HIV prevalence rate"},{"time":32000,"text":"is 1.3 percent among adults."},{"time":35000,"text":"This might not sound like a large number,"},{"time":37000,"text":"but in a country with 76 million people,"},{"time":40000,"text":"it means there are 930,000 that are infected."},{"time":44000,"text":"And due to the poor infrastructure,"},{"time":46000,"text":"only 25 percent of those"},{"time":48000,"text":"are receiving the life-saving drugs that they need."},{"time":51000,"text":"Which is why, in part,"},{"time":53000,"text":"donor agencies provide condoms"},{"time":55000,"text":"at low or no cost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"And so while I was in the DRC,"},{"time":59000,"text":"I spent a lot of time talking to people about condoms,"},{"time":61000,"text":"including Damien."},{"time":63000,"text":"Damien runs a hotel outside of Kinshasa."},{"time":66000,"text":"It's a hotel that's only open until midnight,"},{"time":68000,"text":"so it's not a place that you stay."},{"time":70000,"text":"But it is a place where sex workers and their clients come."},{"time":74000,"text":"Now Damien knows all about condoms,"},{"time":76000,"text":"but he doesn't sell them."},{"time":78000,"text":"He said there's just not in demand."},{"time":80000,"text":"It's not surprising,"},{"time":82000,"text":"because only three percent of people in the DRC"},{"time":84000,"text":"use condoms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"Joseph and Christine,"},{"time":88000,"text":"who run a pharmacy where they sell a number of these condoms,"},{"time":90000,"text":"said despite the fact that donor agencies provide them at low or no cost,"},{"time":94000,"text":"and they have marketing campaigns that go along with them,"},{"time":97000,"text":"their customers don't buy the branded versions."},{"time":100000,"text":"They like the generics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"And as a marketer, I found that curious."},{"time":105000,"text":"And so I started to look at what the marketing looked like."},{"time":108000,"text":"And it turns out that there are three main messages"},{"time":111000,"text":"used by the donor agencies for these condoms:"},{"time":115000,"text":"fear, financing and fidelity."},{"time":119000,"text":"They name the condoms things like Vive, \"to live\""},{"time":123000,"text":"or Trust."},{"time":125000,"text":"They package it with the red ribbon"},{"time":127000,"text":"that reminds us of HIV,"},{"time":129000,"text":"put it in boxes that remind you who paid for them,"},{"time":133000,"text":"show pictures of your wife or husband"},{"time":135000,"text":"and tell you to protect them"},{"time":137000,"text":"or to act prudently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"Now these are not the kinds of things that someone is thinking about"},{"time":143000,"text":"just before they go get a condom."},{"time":145000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":149000,"text":"What is it that you think about"},{"time":151000,"text":"just before you get a condom?"},{"time":153000,"text":"Sex!"},{"time":156000,"text":"And the private companies that sell condoms in these places,"},{"time":159000,"text":"they understand this."},{"time":161000,"text":"Their marketing is slightly different."},{"time":164000,"text":"The name might not be much different,"},{"time":166000,"text":"but the imagery sure is."},{"time":168000,"text":"Some brands are aspirational,"},{"time":171000,"text":"and certainly the packaging is incredibly provocative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"And this made me think"},{"time":177000,"text":"that perhaps the donor agencies had just missed out"},{"time":180000,"text":"on a key aspect of marketing:"},{"time":182000,"text":"understanding who's the audience."},{"time":185000,"text":"And for donor agencies, unfortunately,"},{"time":188000,"text":"the audience tends to be"},{"time":190000,"text":"people that aren't even in the country they're working [in]."},{"time":192000,"text":"It's people back home,"},{"time":194000,"text":"people that support their work,"},{"time":196000,"text":"people like these."},{"time":199000,"text":"But if what we're really trying to do"},{"time":201000,"text":"is stop the spread of HIV,"},{"time":204000,"text":"we need to think about the customer,"},{"time":206000,"text":"the people whose behavior needs to change --"},{"time":209000,"text":"the couples,"},{"time":211000,"text":"the young women, the young men --"},{"time":213000,"text":"whose lives depend on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"And so the lesson is this:"},{"time":218000,"text":"it doesn't really matter what you're selling;"},{"time":221000,"text":"you just have to think about who is your customer,"},{"time":224000,"text":"and what are the messages"},{"time":226000,"text":"that are going to get them to change their behavior."},{"time":228000,"text":"It might just save their lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}